missions/vasseur-pressure/MISSION-COMPLETE.md:58:**Conclusion:** The Vasseur pressure gap cannot be closed by any method that (a) works within the Leray-Hopf energy class and (b) uses H^1 structure of pressure. The gap requires either a regularity gain beyond W^{1,2}, an approach that doesn't pair pressure against De Giorgi test functions, or abandoning the De Giorgi framework.
