missions/navier-stokes/library-inbox/vasseur-2007-proof-architecture.md:188:| Localization method | Explicit cutoff ╬Ę_r, generates error terms via Riesz | Compactness/contradiction: no explicit ╬Ą formula | Fixed-scale De Giorgi iteration: level sets on Q_k ŌåÆ Q_Ōł× |
