missions/navier-stokes/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-003/GOAL.md:5:Analyze Alexis Vasseur's proof (2007) of partial regularity for Navier-Stokes using De Giorgi iteration. Extract the structural features that determine the dimension bound on the singular set, with particular attention to how Vasseur's approach differs from CKN (1982) and Lin (1998).
