missions/navier-stokes/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-003/REPORT.md:115:**Lemma 4** (standard De Giorgi iteration lemma): For C > 1 and ╬▓ > 1, there exists CŌéĆ* such that if WŌéĆ Ōēż CŌéĆ* and for every k Ōēź 1:
