missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md:146:| "H^1 + De Giorgi route is unexploited" | **CORRECTED** | Extensively developed by Vasseur school, H^1 used since 2007. BUT: H^1-BMO duality with De Giorgi test functions (the specific Step 2B angle) appears NOT to have been tried |
