missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md:360:The idea: construct a corrector w_k such that div(Žå_k u - w_k) = 0. Then the modified test function is divergence-free, and Ōł½ p ┬Ę div(...) = 0 ŌĆö the pressure term vanishes.
