+# Normalize Notation And Name The Operative Bound Up Front
+
+If copied notes use varying sign or normalization conventions, require the
+explorer to normalize notation at the start.
+
+If both schematic and concrete bounds appear in the source trail, also require
+the explorer to state which bound the branch is actually using. Otherwise later
+summaries can preserve the wrong obstruction.
+
+Filed from:
